<author>bạsm sẖkry, bhjt ʿdly</author>
<title>ʿmrk msẖ mḍmwn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿmrk msẖ mḍmwn fy ạ̹ydyk .. wfy lḥẓạt ạlnạs btmwt
 ṣwt ạlrb ynạdy ʿlyk .. wfy kl mrẗ ạlfrṣẗ tfwt)2
 ạlqrạr- (qwl lh ạ̹rḥmny kfạyẗ bʿạd .. slm kl ḥyạtk lyh
 lyh tfḍl ʿạysẖ fy ʿnạd .. dh ạlʿmr ạlmḍmwn fy ạ̹ydyh)2
 2- (ạ̹yh fy ạlʿạlm gẖyr ạlḍyq .. lyh rạfḍ tsmʿ llṣwt
 ạ̉ʿẓm ạ̉kẖ wạ̉wfy̱ ṣdyq .. msẖ hạyfydk bʿd ạlmwt)2
 3- (rạḥ tndm ʿly̱ ʿmr tẖmyn .. ndmk msẖ hạykwn lh ḥdwd
 tṣrkẖ fy ạlạ̉bdyẗ lmyn .. frṣẗ wḍạʿt msẖ hạtʿwd)2</lyrics>
</song>